🕉️✨ A Journey Within… ✨🕉️
From the divine ghats of Varanasi to the sacred vibes of Ayodhya, Naimisharanya, Chitrakoot, Prayagraj, and Kashi Vishwanath every step felt like a blessing, every moment brought peace to my soul. 🙏
Ye safar sirf ek trip nahi tha… ek anubhav tha, jo man aur atma dono ko shanti de gaya 🌿
Sharing some glimpses of this sacred journey through these pictures each one holding a memory, a prayer, and divine energy. 💫
